# ON3KRB Personal Website

Welcome to the ON3KRB personal website! This site is dedicated to sharing information about continuous wave (CW) operations, portable setups, and other personal projects. Below is a detailed breakdown of the different sections available on the site.

## Pages Overview

### 1. Continuous Wave (CW)
This section covers various aspects of continuous wave radio operation. You'll find information on:
- Basics of CW
- Operating procedures
- Station setup
- Recommended gear and antennas

### 2. Mobile
The mobile section focuses on equipment and setups for operating radio from a vehicle. This includes:
- Vehicle modifications for radio operations
- Recommended mobile radios and antennas
- Tips for effective mobile operation

### 3. Portable
In this section, you'll learn about portable radio setups, ideal for use in the field. Topics include:
- Lightweight equipment recommendations
- Setup for field operations
- Best practices and tips for portable operation

### 4. Shack Setups
This page showcases various home radio stations (shacks) including:
- Station layouts
- Equipment lists
- Personal stories about each setup

### 5. Blog
The blog section features articles on:
- Personal experiences
- Tips and tricks for radio enthusiasts
- Updates on new projects and gear

### 6. Contact Information
For inquiries, feedback, or collaborations, please use the contact information provided:
- Email: on3krb@example.com (replace with actual email)
- Social media links (if applicable)

## Conclusion
Thank you for visiting my personal website! I hope you find the information helpful and engaging. Feel free to reach out with any questions or comments!
